cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image analysis and segmentation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of statistical ranking and probabilistic interpretation suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) techniques. The application of the method to medical imaging data suggests the involvement of medical imaging (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of tracking and decision-making algorithms suggests the involvement of robotics and control (cs.NE) sub-category.
